main event: A report from July 7, 1947, describes a crashed unidentified flying object in Lakeland, Florida.
interesting points: The report includes a black and white photograph of the crashed UFO,The object has a distinctive shape with angled structures,The photograph depicts the UFO lying on the ground in an outdoor setting,The report is labeled as 'EARLY A UNCLASSIFIED',The incident occurred shortly after the famous Roswell incident.
